    <data key="d0">AWS Serverless Architectures (Food Hub, Freightways, Vertex Pharmaceuticals)</data>
    <data key="d1">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=m4HbkhRw4UE</data>
    <data key="d2">This architecture consolidates three distinct customer solutions leveraging AWS serverless technologies. Food Hub handles high-scale order processing and real-time dashboarding with Lambda, DynamoDB, Kinesis, S3, and QuickSight. Freightways uses Fargate, DynamoDB, Lambda, SNS, and SQS for a scalable package tracking system, managing 1500 scans per minute. Vertex Pharmaceuticals built an intelligent molecule search platform using API Gateway, Lambda, RDS, ECS (Fargate orchestrator and workers), and Amazon MQ with RabbitMQ for computational chemistry, dynamically spinning up resources for tens of billions of potential molecules.</data>
    <data key="d3">data_ingestion, interactive, compute_intensive, control</data>
    <data key="d4">True</data>
  </graph>
</graphml>
